; Coverage test for post.cc get_account when account is not found (L296-297).
; account("Nonexistent") should throw an error when the named account
; doesn't exist in the journal.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --limit "account('Nonexistent')" -> 1
__ERROR__
While evaluating value expression:
  account("Nonexistent")
  ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
While calling function 'account Nonexistent':
While handling posting from "$FILE", line 6:
>     Expenses:Food    $10.00
Error: Could not find an account matching 'Nonexistent'
end test
